These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, tomato
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, photography
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, time-travel
1. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the person eating tomato##8
2. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
3. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola      |
| Food          | tomato | pumpkin    |
| Hobby         | photography   | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | time-travel      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, 7up
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, cooking
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, engineer
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, train
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
3. the engineer is not to the right of the freelancer##8
4. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person who's hobby is cooking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | water        | 7up    |
| Hobby       | board-games         | cooking |
| Job         | engineer | freelancer   |
| Transport   | quad-bike               | train  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, horror
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, punk
There are 2 different nationalities: german, malaysian
2 different pets are kept: snake, mouse
1. the german is in an odd position##4
2. the malaysian is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire       | horror |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk    |
| Nationality   | german | malaysian |
| Pet           | snake        | mouse   |

 #################################

 
