2. the person driving the helicopter is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
4. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
5. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person eating strawberry##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
