The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the american is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person driving the boat is not the person watching western movies##6
4. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
